items.title: [Macri] According to a league source, the Knicks have several notable players in for a workout today, incl. fast rising UVA wing Trey Murphy III, Florida G Tre Mann & Kentucky C Isaiah Jackson. Murphy & Jackson are on the short list for the final 2 spots in the Green Room next Thursday.
